    "title": "Junior SEO Specialist at Bewakoof",
    "description": "Grow your career with Bewakoof! We are hiring a SEO Specialist for our Amritsar team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Bewakoof:\nBewakoof is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Amritsar, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Bewakoof!",
